#

Pumpkin Seed Chocolate Bark

10 min
$5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy (if using chocolate with soy lecithin)

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeVegan

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack

Tags:

SnackDessertEasy

Description

A delightful and crunchy chocolate treat topped with nutritious pumpkin seeds, perfect for snacking!

Ingredients

  • dark chocolate chips: 1 cup
  • pumpkin seeds: 1/2 cup
  • sea salt: a pinch
  • vanilla extract (optional): 1/2 tsp
